<br>
Actually, from all the tests I've seen, faster weapons do more damage over time. Not sure why. The miss rate seems to be lower, and the proc rate is significantly higher.<br>
<br>
Example:<br>
<br>
You hit with a 6.0 spd weapon 10 times for 100 damage each time, and it procs for 25 damage 5 times. You've done 600 + 125 damage.<br>
<br>
You hit with a 3.0 spd weapon 20 times for 50 damage each time, and it procs for 25 damage 10 times. You've done 600 + 250 damage. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <br><font color=#000000>- </font><a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/blighttanksofdaoc>Light Tanks of DAoC</a><font color=#000000> - </font><a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm6>Blademaster Equipment</a> <font color=#000000> - </font><br><br><br><br>Powered By <a href=http://www.ezboard.com/>ezboard®</a> Ver. 7.245d<br>Copyright ©1999-2003 ezboard, Inc.</center></body></html>  

